cat << EOF
ATA S.M.A.R.T. (i.e. hard disk health monitoring) reader and parser.
libatasmart: a lean, small and clean implementation of an ATA S.M.A.R.T.
        reading and parsing library.
skdump: a little tool that produces a similar output  to smartctl -a, but uses
        libatasmart.
sktest: a little tool for starting/aborting S.M.A.R.T. self-tests, based on
        libatasmart.
